{"type": "article", "id": 5201, "title": "Teddyfish X Kapok 联名包袋系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-14T07:39:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233455rXDx7J01fksBmcAu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，香港生活方式潮牌 Kapok 联手法国包袋品牌 Teddyfish 推出联名系列包袋，包含一款双肩背包以及大、小两款手包单品。设计团队以木棉为设计主题，做出了别致的花朵迷彩图案，搭配以浅灰与深蓝两种背景主色调，透出素净的美感。帆布与 wickett &amp; craig 特质过蜡皮革的使用，也赋予了这一系列包袋防水特性，。此外，双肩背包内部还专门设计了加厚隔层，可容纳一台 13 英寸的 macbook 笔记本电脑。定价 490－2390 港币（约合人民币 392－1911 元）不等，<a href=\"http://www.ka-pok.com/webshop/designers/q-to-t/teddyfish.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334538UDx2b0vpJOomhAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233453UG6SVZC2XcLNjWbH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233454vNAR8pxDGyMsBd29.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233454Ig8WlVr3KoG4MpHa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}